*.ogg   binary -text diff
*.otf   binary -text diff
*.pdf   binary -text diff
*.phar  binary -text diff
*.png   binary -text diff
*.rar   binary -text diff
*.svgz  binary -text diff   
*.tar*  binary -text diff
